# ============================================================
# .gitignore — zeus-co marketplace
# Proteção: nada sensível deve subir pro GitHub
# ============================================================

# macOS
.DS_Store
*.swp
._*

# Credenciais NUNCA aqui
*.env
*.env.local
**/credentials.json
**/secrets/
**/.htpasswd

# Backups (não pertencem ao marketplace)
**/backups/
**/_Publicacoes/Backup/
**/findash_data.json
**/users.json
**/api/dados.json

# Logs
**/*.log
**/.logs/

# Editor / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml

# Plugin binários
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Ferramentas Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/

# Permitir docs explicitamente
!**/SKILL.md
!**/CORE.md
!**/LITERATURE.md
!**/RADAR.md
!**/EVOLUTION.md
!**/WEEKLY_DIGEST.md
!**/templates/*.md
!**/README.md
!**/plugin.json
!**/marketplace.json
